{"tid":1383521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[[[召集]]]自己香港自己救，冷氣軍師出良謀!","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:08:20.000Z","uid":229994,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68867f03c6c614b278a5d3e857aad1415f7ed004","tid":1383521,"uid":229994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"救港嘅唔係HKSARCEO/AO/EO，可能就係我地一班冷氣軍師。計策方向並非絕對正確，但需要討論救港，希望大家集思廣益。<br />\n<br />\n1. 統率性：冇大台嘅弊端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，談判能力近乎零。以顏色為主導搭台，一來可以有系統將不同人士歸邊行動，二來有台有代表增強對不同party嘅談判能力，三來有效地過濾假消息統一發佈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 階段性：有冇諗過分訴求都可以分階段進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一刀切訴求係好霸氣，但諗下就知幾乎無可能實行，倒不如設下時間線，逐個訴求去傾，呢樣唔得，OK! 先退一退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；呢樣有空間，OK! 嘗試爭取更多嘅合理要求。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 目標性：究竟係想對準一個人？一個部門？一個政策？一個政權？定一個國家體系？以哲學思想出發，事情由小至大，由下而上，由內到外，逐步向目標進發而唔係一步登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n憤怒過後要理性救港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9bcbee475a343cb1376beba7a06f8fbe9fd237","tid":1383521,"uid":110851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師幫幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"0fb44967c49c5ab9b171a8800206e3ef937c18f5","tid":1383521,"uid":229994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"冷集軍師Assemble!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.